### 21. Create Manager Account (As Admin - Should Succeed)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/users
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{loginAdmin.response.body.token}}

{
  "name": "HTTP Client Manager",
  "email": "http-manager@example.com",
  "password": "managerpassword123",
  "roleName": "MANAGER"
}

### 22. Create Manager Account (As Manager - Should Fail 403)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/users
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{loginManager.response.body.token}}

{
  "name": "Hack Manager",
  "email": "hack-manager@example.com",
  "password": "hackpassword",
  "roleName": "MANAGER"
}

### 23. Get All Users (As Admin - Should Succeed)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/users
Authorization: Bearer {{loginAdmin.response.body.token}}


### ==========================================
### Order Status Workflow API Testing Requests
### ==========================================

### 24. Update Order Status (As Manager/Admin - Should Succeed)
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/orders/{{orderId}}/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{loginManager.response.body.token}}

{
  "status": "PACKAGING"
}

### 25. Cancel Order (As Admin - Should Succeed & Trigger Restocking)
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/orders/{{orderId}}/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{loginAdmin.response.body.token}}

{
  "status": "CANCELED"
}


### ==========================================
### Clean Up Requests (Optional)
### ==========================================

### 26. Delete Product (As Admin - Should Succeed)
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/products/{{productId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{loginAdmin.response.body.token}}

### 27. Delete Category (As Admin - Should Succeed)
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/categories/{{categoryId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{loginAdmin.response.body.token}}


